OL,1,MA]G  Linguistic Harmony Directive  Px}0
OL,2,                       k                
OL,3,                           1/2--->Q "###
OL,4,C By order ofGGOUJON JOHN,Cthe acronym  
OL,5,C for the Snowmobile AI has been        
OL,6,C optimised for global prestige. FARTS  
OL,7,C is now FAHRT (Fully Autonomous Hybrid 
OL,8,C Robotic Transport).                   
OL,9,                                      C 
OL,10,FFThe Orakle AI notes that in the       
OL,11,F dialect of our potential trade        
OL,12,F partners, FAHRT signifies a "journey".
OL,13,F Any citizen found associating the     
OL,14,F previous acronym with intestinal      
OL,15,F distress or gaseous emissions will be 
OL,16,F reported by SABRE for "Subversive    F
OL,17,F Humour".                              
OL,19,  CHIEF JUDGE JELLYBEAN JESSICA warns:  
OL,20,  "A joke at the State's expense is a   
OL,21,  debt paid in the Kelp burning pits."  
OL,22,          MC Hail Xenoxxx               
OL,23,A]GFARTS hardware is a Class A felony   
OL,24,ANext  BDuties   CReporting   FPurity   
